    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Comparison of the forelegs of Karatau mesomantispines. A. Karataumantispa carnaria. B. Longicollum benmaddoxi gen. et sp. nov. C. Ovalofemora monstruosa comb. nov. D. Ovalofemora abbottae gen. et sp. nov. Scale bars 1 mm. Drawings of forelegs of Karatau mesomantispines, not to scale. E. Karataumantispa carnaria. F. Longicollum benmaddoxi gen. et sp. nov. G. Ovalofemora monstruosa comb. nov.H. Ovalofemora abbottaegen. et sp. nov." ;
